unexplained within the standard\naccretion-jet framework and appears to be markedly different to similar\npatterns of behavior in X-ray binaries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Nov 2016 21:24:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-01"}
