g the 4 year observation campaign. We confirm previous\nmeasurements of the VHE spectrum of Sagittarius A*, and do not detect any\nsignificant variability of the emission from the source. Furthermore, the known\nVHE gamma-ray emitter at the location of the supernova remnant G0.9+0.1 was\ndetected, as well as the recently discovered VHE source close to the GG radio\nArc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Nov 2016 23:13:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-09"}
